                           Project 2 - Cobinational Chips
                           ------------------------------
  

Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.
HalfAdder.hdl - sums 2 bits.
FullAdder.hdl - sums 3 bits.
Add16.hdl - Adds two 16-bit values.
Inc16.hdl - increments a 16 bit number (arithmetically).
ALU.hdl - an arithmatic logic unit.
ShiftLeft.hdl - doubles a 16 bit number.
ShiftRight.hdl - divides a 16 bit number by 2.
Mul.hdl - multiplies 2 16 bit nubers.

